  "id": "RAW_907b3b04",
  "title": "JetBrains 放弃 Fleet：急刹变道打造全新 Agentic IDE，与 VS Code、Cursor 争夺下一代 AI 编程王座",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1NDA4NjU2MA==&mid=2247651186&idx=2&sn=c8ae866b9153d42b8f2ed90efffc08d7",
  "date": "2025-12-14 05:30:00",
  "author": "AI前线",
  "siteName": "AI前线",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(145, 145, 145);white-space:normal;font-weight:normal;font-size:14px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 14px;margin:13px 0px 0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">编译 | Tina</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(89, 89, 89);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:15px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:19px;margin:24px 8px 0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">VS Code、Cursor 打得火热，JetBrains 扛不住了？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">本周，JetBrains 宣布停止开发 Fleet 这款 IDE。该产品自 2021 年推出以来一直停留在公开预览阶段，从未真正“转正”。接下来，公司将把更多精力投入到一款面向智能体（agentic）开发的全新开发环境 Air 上。</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503782478\" data-ratio=\"1.0163666121112929\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;vertical-align: bottom;height: auto !important;width: 661px !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"611\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c2f05a57&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FYriaiaJPb26VPhd6kicD0icKLP8DnNb0AHzibUVaIAM9kBGxwrrSFVc03eQKkYSNibicH1hicPia5VETqzDGUnpq7ZjWYkw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D1\"></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">JetBrains 旗下有一整套 IDE 产品线，但大多都基于同一个 IntelliJ 核心平台，该平台运行在 JVM（Java 虚拟机）之上。旗舰产品 IntelliJ IDEA 最早发布于 2001 年，至今已经快 25 年。几年前，JetBrains 觉得有必要重新做一款从零设计的新产品：更轻量、更适合协作，对远程项目也要做到一流支持。与此同时，微软的 Visual Studio Code（VS Code）正是凭借这些特性迅速崛起，给 JetBrains 带来了不小压力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">当时 JetBrains 的规划是：一方面继续演进基于 IntelliJ 的传统 IDE，另一方面推出一款全新架构的 Fleet。官方在首发博文中强调，Fleet 是“从零起步打造的新架构和新界面”。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Fleet 确实赢得了一部分开发者的青睐，但大多数人依然难以从熟悉的 IntelliJ 系列上“挪窝”。IntelliJ 完整的插件生态，以及 Fleet 长期处于“永远公测”的状态，都是原因之一。今年 2 月，JetBrains 发布了一款基于 Fleet 的 Kotlin Multiplatform 跨平台开发 IDE，但很快就被砍掉，改为加强 IntelliJ 对该场景的支持。当时外界就已开始怀疑 Fleet 本身还能撑多久。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">事实证明，这些担忧不无道理。JetBrains 本周在公告中表示：“自 2025 年 12 月 22 日起，Fleet 将不再提供下载。我们正在打造一款聚焦智能体开发的新产品。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">公司给出的解释是：维持两条 IDE 产品线既容易让用户困惑，也分散了内部精力。“我们既没能用 Fleet 取代 IntelliJ IDEA，也没能把它收窄到一个清晰、差异化的细分赛道。”IntelliJ IDEA 负责人 Aleksey Stukalov 和产品经理 Ekaterina Prigara 写道。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">并且，随着人工智能技术的成熟，他们曾探索过将 Fleet 打造成一款以人工智能为核心的编辑器，但“最终确认，再推出一款人工智能编辑器并不会脱颖而出，尤其是在充斥着大量以人工智能为核心的 VS Code 分支的市场中。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">他们同时强调，Fleet 是一次有价值的尝试，其多个组件现已被整合进 JetBrains 其他 IDE 中。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">严格来说，Fleet 也并非彻底“死亡”。目前处于公测阶段的全新智能体开发产品 Air，就是基于 Fleet 平台演化而来，但针对的是一种全新的工作流。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">“我们越来越清楚地认识到，最佳方案是强化现有 IDE 中的人工智能工作流程。然而，人工智能的飞速发展揭示了 Fleet 更为契合的另一个细分市场。”这个细分市场看起来是这样的：</span></p>\n  <div data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"94875\" data-width=\"98%\" style=\"width: 98%;flex: 0 0 98%;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;box-sizing:border-box;max-width:98% !important;\">\n    <div style=\"display: flex;\">\n     <div style=\"display: flex;\">\n      <div data-autoskip=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;padding-left:10px;font-size: 14px;color:#333;letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-align: justify;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px;display: block;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"caret-color: red;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">当我们在编辑器中探索 AI 能力时，一种全新的开发工作流也开始逐渐成形。开发者开始将真正重要的任务交给智能体（agent）处理——更新测试、清理代码、重构模块、探索陌生代码路径，甚至构建全新的功能。这些任务会异步运行，并直接返回完整的补丁。开发者不再亲自写代码，而是负责指导智能体、并审阅其产出。这与经典 IDE 的工作流有着本质区别：传统模式基于即时反馈、同步控制，以及一个稳定的本地状态。</span></span></span></p>\n       <div>\n        <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">智能体式（agentic）循环依赖于结构化的任务定义、上下文组装、多轮异步执行、隔离的运行环境，以及“审阅优先（review-first）”的工作方式。要在一个单一工具中把这些全部整合，会带来割裂的体验。因此，Fleet 团队选择不再继续与传统 IDE 和代码编辑器竞争，而是转向打造一款专注于智能体工作流的新产品：智能体开发环境（agentic development environment）。这一全新的环境以 Fleet 平台为基础，但将以全新产品、全新名称的方式发布。技术、团队和长期方向都会延续，但产品身份与目标市场将发生变化。</span></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Air 目前已开放公测，但使用需要绑定 Anthropic 订阅。规划中的功能包括：支持 Windows 和 Linux（目前仅完全支持 macOS）、在浏览器中运行、接入更多智能体（如 Codex、Gemini、Junie），以及云端执行模式，让 Air 在开发者离线后依然可以在云端继续运行。</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503782481\" data-ratio=\"0.6342592592592593\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;vertical-align: bottom;height: auto !important;width: 661px !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8453e46e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FYriaiaJPb26VPhd6kicD0icKLP8DnNb0AHzibtKAd6sJDIodQs4iadP9kIdcY3rcE3sXzBPU7LibLQRrx70LO4nx6UxdA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D2\"></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">喜欢 Fleet 的开发者难免感到失落。“这是一个错误决定。Fleet 原本有机会把 JetBrains 优秀的工具链带进一个可以对标 VS Code（以及如今的 Zed）的新产品……”有用户如此吐槽。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503782480\" data-ratio=\"0.5167037861915368\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;vertical-align: bottom;height: auto !important;width: 661px !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"898\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=32feb84f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FYriaiaJPb26VPhd6kicD0icKLP8DnNb0AHziblFwibvAAfolB6rjiaDGoawYgdakRnianeOM5VFvkj2Wpbqrxfo83QOQZA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D3\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503782479\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.30286343612334804\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"908\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;vertical-align: bottom;height: auto !important;width: 661px !important;visibility: visible !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7bb96c57&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FYriaiaJPb26VPhd6kicD0icKLP8DnNb0AHzibROicMgQoFDncRVjEIZOEgmQ64YzJBjFkkR2D1jI1GWVZ1EBzPPOCaOQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D4\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">把时间线拉长看，这其实是一种重复出现的模式：Fleet 的定位是和 VS Code 竞争，而 Air 则是瞄准新一波 AI 编程工具，包括 AWS Kiro、Google Antigravity、Cursor 等。微软的 VS Code 自身也已经转向以 AI 为中心。</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">为了跟上软件开发范式的变化，JetBrains 再一次选择打造一款全新产品。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">不过，也有开发者质疑：真的有必要重造一遍轮子吗？“我更希望 JetBrains 能在自家那些‘重型 IDE’的优势之上叠加智能体功能，而不是重新做一个工具。”一位开发者表示。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">如何说服开发者从现有工具迁移到 Air，上一次 JetBrains 没能说动他们改用 Fleet，这一次恐怕也不会轻松。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: bold;\">参考链接：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://devclass.com/2025/12/09/jetbrains-abandons-fleet-ide-pins-hopes-on-forthcoming-air-agentic-development-tool/\" target=\"_blank\">https://devclass.com/2025/12/09/jetbrains-abandons-fleet-ide-pins-hopes-on-forthcoming-air-agentic-development-tool/</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://blog.jetbrains.com/fleet/2025/12/the-future-of-fleet/\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.jetbrains.com/fleet/2025/12/the-future-of-fleet/</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "JetBrains 宣布终止轻量级 IDE Fleet 的开发，转而聚焦于基于 Fleet 平台、面向智能体（Agentic）开发的全新 IDE 产品 Air，以争夺下一代 AI 编程市场的领导地位。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "JetBrains 宣布终止轻量级 IDE Fleet 的开发，转而聚焦于基于 Fleet 平台、面向智能体（Agentic）开发的全新 IDE 产品 Air，以争夺下一代 AI 编程市场的领导地位。",
  "summary": "文章详细报道了 JetBrains 停止开发其轻量级 IDE Fleet 的决策，并宣布将重心转向代号为 Air 的全新智能体（Agentic）开发环境。Fleet 自 2021 年发布以来一直处于公开预览阶段，未能有效挑战 VS Code 在轻量级编辑器市场的地位，也未能从传统 IntelliJ 系列中吸引足够多的用户。JetBrains 认为，维持两条 IDE 产品线会分散精力，且在 AI 编程工具日益增多的市场中，再打造一款 AI 编辑器已无法脱颖而出。因此，公司决定利用 Fleet 的技术积累，探索全新的智能体驱动开发范式，即由 Agent 异步执行任务、开发者负责指导和审阅的新工作流。Air 目前已开放公测，并计划支持更多 AI 模型和云端执行，旨在与 AWS Kiro、Google Antigravity 等新一代 AI 编程工具竞争，力求在 AI 编程领域取得领先。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "JetBrains 停止开发 Fleet，战略转型聚焦智能体开发",
      "explanation": "Fleet 因未能成功挑战 VS Code 且与现有 IntelliJ 产品线重叠，JetBrains 决定停止其开发。这一战略决策旨在将资源集中于面向智能体（Agentic）开发的新产品 Air，以适应 AI 驱动的全新编程范式和市场竞争。"
    },
    {
      "point": "智能体驱动开发（Agentic Development）定义未来编程新范式",
      "explanation": "Agentic 开发模式的核心是将代码更新、重构、模块探索、特性构建等任务交给 AI 智能体异步执行，开发者则主要负责指导智能体并审阅其产出。这种“审阅优先”的工作方式，以及对结构化任务定义、上下文组装和隔离运行环境的依赖，与传统 IDE 的即时反馈和同步控制模式存在本质区别。"
    },
    {
      "point": "JetBrains 意图通过 Air 抢占 AI 编程市场制高点",
      "explanation": "基于 Fleet 平台演化而来的 Air，是 JetBrains 面对 AI 时代编程范式变革的积极响应。通过对更多 AI 模型（如 Codex、Gemini）和云端执行模式的支持，JetBrains 期望 Air 能有效与 AWS Kiro、Google Antigravity 等新兴 AI 编程工具竞争，从而在快速发展的 AI 编程市场中占据领先地位。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "自 2025 年 12 月 22 日起，Fleet 将不再提供下载。我们正在打造一款聚焦智能体开发的新产品。",
    "我们最终确认，再推出一款人工智能编辑器并不会脱颖而出，尤其是在充斥着大量以人工智能为核心的 VS Code 分支的市场中。",
    "开发者不再亲自写代码，而是负责指导智能体、并审阅其产出。这与经典 IDE 的工作流有着本质区别：传统模式基于即时反馈、同步控制，以及一个稳定的本地状态。"
  ],
